{"tid":731974,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"長期食緊治敏速","createTime":"2018-07-06T15:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T15:12:46.000Z","uid":129166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1887988bfbb5f2c2f314694d2d1628aa4a15e69e","tid":731974,"uid":129166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"上個月開始突然生風癩 <br />\n要食治敏速先唔會好痕同突起啲癩 <br />\n一停藥又會黎料<br />\n食到宜家都未好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有無人知點先可以好返 好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且驚食太多藥會對身體唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9272ece22bda9e3abd1039cc1ac5102ba72b704d","tid":731974,"uid":27008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"你食果隻藥又無乜副作用既<br />\n<br />\n你諗下你身邊有無乜致敏源好過<br />\n雖然天氣都係個因素"},{"pid":"e0efd5763a89de3068b12fe670955a55146f0717","tid":731974,"uid":129166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9272ece22bda9e3abd1039cc1ac5102ba72b704d","tid":731974,"uid":27008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"你食果隻藥又無乜副作用既<br />\n<br />\n你諗下你身邊有無乜致敏源好過<br />\n雖然天氣都係個因素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"我諗緊會唔會係我長期涯夜先會咁<br />\n同埋以往都無對啲咩敏感"},{"pid":"4205dcbaf7020f2778cbb65facc4ac19a4df0c48","tid":731974,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0efd5763a89de3068b12fe670955a55146f0717","tid":731974,"uid":129166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9272ece22bda9e3abd1039cc1ac5102ba72b704d","tid":731974,"uid":27008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"你食果隻藥又無乜副作用既<br />\n<br />\n你諗下你身邊有無乜致敏源好過<br />\n雖然天氣都係個因素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"我諗緊會唔會係我長期涯夜先會咁<br />\n同埋以往都無對啲咩敏感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:51:21.000Z","msg"